data.description: Beautiful spacious modern home that features 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a mud room with a substantial storage room, and an extra living room in the back. As you walk in the front door you are greeted with the main living room, that connects to the very roomy kitchen, that has all the cabinets you can dream of and an island in the middle. The master bedroom has a standard closet and a sizable bathroom with a shower stall and garden tub. The 3 guest bedrooms are located down the hall on the opposite side of the main bedroom. The hallway opens up at the bedroom doors for a less crowded walkway.  At the end of the hall way there is a second living room that is being utilized as a work out area. This additional room has so much space for activities. Within the 2.5 acres there is a fenced off grassy backyard, and a cozy grass lawn in the front. Must see property with must see views.
